==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: mummify
<hw>mum"mi*fy</hw> <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To turn into a mummy-like
corpse; to dry up with unusually little decomposition; -- said of dead
animals; <as>as, A <ex>mummified</ex> body was found in the
attic</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mummy</ent>⟦br⟧
